595
00:40:36,434 --> 00:40:39,396
<i>'Cause way down deep inside
I've got a dream</i>

596
00:40:39,437 --> 00:40:41,273
<i>- I've got</i> a <i>dream</i>
- ALL: <i>He's got</i> a <i>dream</i>

597
00:40:41,356 --> 00:40:43,275
<i>- I've got a dream
- He's got a dream</i>

598
00:40:43,358 --> 00:40:46,736
<i>And I know one day
romance will reign supreme</i>

599
00:40:46,778 --> 00:40:48,697
