609
00:41:17,893 --> 00:41:19,144
What's your dream?

610
00:41:19,227 --> 00:41:22,147
No, no, no. Sorry, boys. I don't sing.

611
00:41:23,398 --> 00:41:25,400
<i>(SINGING) I have dreams like you
No, really</i>

612
00:41:25,483 --> 00:41:27,068
<i>Just much less touchy-feely</i>

613
00:41:27,152 --> 00:41:30,196
<i>They mainly happen
somewhere warm and sunny</i>

614
00:41:30,280 --> 00:41:33,909
<i>On an island that I own
