615
00:41:34,993 --> 00:41:37,996
<i>Surrounded by enormous
piles of money</i>

616
00:41:38,038 --> 00:41:39,956
<i>- I've got</i> a <i>dream</i>
- ALL: <i>She's got</i> a <i>dream</i>

617
00:41:39,998 --> 00:41:41,750
<i>- I've got a dream
- She's got a dream</i>

618
00:41:41,833 --> 00:41:44,336
<i>I just want to see
the floating lanterns gleam</i>

619
00:41:44,419 --> 00:41:45,503
