675
00:44:57,862 --> 00:44:59,239
- Chameleon.
- Nuance.

676
00:44:59,531 --> 00:45:04,035
Here's my question, though,
if you want to see the lanterns so badly

677
00:45:04,119 --> 00:45:06,037
why haven't you gone before?

678
00:45:06,329 --> 00:45:08,123
Uh... (CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)

679
